      "operation": "NOT INCLUDED",
      "pPageRef": "G33",
      "description": "Calibrating ADAS sensors using stationary targets in a controlled environment.",
      "steps": [
        "Position vehicle on level surface",
        "Verify tire pressure at OEM spec",
        "Verify vehicle height (fuel level, no cargo)",
